islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:23:23.000Z","msg":"但係SHAW 同馬仔,福仔係咪V92 時期出黎?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:25:11.000Z","msg":"係呀"},{"pid":"e4fe508c42a428af6060ec575a57b37a02f26c72","tid":940383,"uid":58863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:28:30.000Z","msg":"摩佬同爺爺既差距愈黎愈大了"},{"pid":"dae1e687a986eede0b33e3074a222e7b805e069f","tid":940383,"uid":9217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:29:03.000Z","msg":"名宿收左錢要幫現任領隊護航"},{"pid":"5727bdd6543a9266383918782829ebd0ef2ca9a5","tid":940383,"uid":27591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:31:49.000Z","msg":"痴線仲講緊莫耶斯"},{"pid":"8082cc84dd06ec204da391183beb58de0536089f","tid":940383,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:36:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5716113&amp;&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D5716113%26%26page%3D1&d=Xm7WKmrItRA9qTfGUjZ%2Fa54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=cc14a30d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5716113&amp;&amp;page=1</a>"},{"pid":"59da43dfae01d6afec73b527977874585fe86fab","tid":940383,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:39:02.000Z","msg":"曼聯官方廣告寸爆莫耶斯！<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Xm7WKmrItRA9qTfGUjZ%2Fa54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b9b714f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯官方電視頻道（MUTV）播出廣告為新球季造勢，但竟然拿上季領隊莫耶斯來祭旗，結果遭到網民劣評，廣告亦已停播。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》報道，廣告一開始，陰沉密雲的天空上出現「被欽點者」（The Chosen One）的橫額，配上莫耶斯（David Moyes）的頭像，下面再加一行細字：「經過一個令人失望的球季之後&hellip;&hellip;」，配音亦絕不留情，一把蘇格蘭口音的男聲說：「見鬼的比賽，到底搞什麼鬼！」一把女聲就說：「我以他們為恥！」<br />\n<br />\n之後一眾曼聯球員從烏雲中走出來，配上「我們會捲土重來」的字樣，配音則是「相信我們吧，我們會重新上路」，還有傑斯的聲音：「繼續支持我們吧，好日子即將重來！」之後出現畢樹比、費格遜等名宿的雕像，最後新帥雲高爾、副手傑斯出現，字幕是「大師與學徒」（Master &amp; Apprentice）。<br />\n<br />\n整段片的訊息很清楚，就是在經歷「莫耶斯之亂」之後，曼聯會在雲高爾和傑斯的帶領下重拾昔日光輝。畢竟莫耶斯也是球隊上任教練，曼聯今次將莫帥「擺上枱」，實在有欠厚道，《都市報》指在twitter上廣告廣受抨擊，被轟為「無品」，而廣告亦已迅速被移走。<br />\n<br />\n51歲的莫斯斯，現時仍未有班落，早前更被指在酒吧內打人，但他一於少理，日前現身正在舉行英國公開賽的皇家利物浦高爾夫球俱樂部，心情似乎十分輕鬆。"},{"pid":"27f7596c6922f09a47bef8866ea2a66a27a9a82c","tid":940383,"uid":100766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"80ff1e404f764f08c5baa24ad2b1cfc1807a0f3f","tid":940383,"uid":45428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"af059b49132e365d35cc72db06c2a01bc6c7cd1c","tid":940383,"uid":100766,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:21:40.000Z","msg":"聽講摩狗而家仲用緊椰子同雲膠爾留低+操起嘅球員吊緊命<br />\n<br />\nMata<br />\n爆炸頭<br />\nRashford<br />\nMartial<br />\nDe Gea<br />\n<br />\n仲未計後防仍然係左羊右華<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啲所謂名宿淨係識踢波<br />\n睇波就用屎眼睇架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:24:06.000Z","msg":"佢在位簽果d 山狗 lkk 連迪洛夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:40:34.000Z","msg":"條撚樣真係唔識架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eead9cabf95fbc0b2abc4c28e677b7ce3f22c5c6","tid":940383,"uid":100766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a02aea276bad1847e15348529d18ca4f53ea4c77","tid":940383,"uid":45428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"942cdb111c22bc3ca11dbd01005d52b5abac93b3","tid":940383,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af059b49132e365d35cc72db06c2a01bc6c7cd1c","tid":940383,"uid":100766,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:21:40.000Z","msg":"聽講摩狗而家仲用緊椰子同雲膠爾留低+操起嘅球員吊緊命<br />\n<br />\nMata<br />\n爆炸頭<br />\nRashford<br />\nMartial<br />\nDe Gea<br />\n<br />\n仲未計後防仍然係左羊右華<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啲所謂名宿淨係識踢波<br />\n睇波就用屎眼睇架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\